{"tid":1601920,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「警察封鎖線」其實市民係可以進入！","createTime":"2019-09-29T08:33:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-01T14:33:34.000Z","uid":190817,"like":32,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"33495ed57ee56a61e9ea4d6c8ec72c9f39247355","tid":1601920,"uid":190817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T08:33:45.000Z","msg":"我好奇點解每次差佬封鎖線，都可以亂咁拉？<br />\n之後，上網搵左資料。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n結果<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">市民係可以入到警察封鎖區</span></span><br />\n<br />\n根據2013年謝律師的文章：<br />\n<br />\n除了「公安條例」，我找不到其他法例，賦予警察一般權力，在公眾地方設置「封鎖區」。<br />\n<br />\n3、根據「公安條例」第17條4節，即使警察有權「阻截和封閉」通道，仍只適用於違規的公眾集會（50人以上）或遊行（30人以上），<span style=\"color: red;\">不適用於一般或其他情況</span>。 <br />\n<br />\n4、就林老師事件，不少批評者指她不應進入或逗留在「封瑣區」，甚至指這是違法行爲。「應該與否」是道德價值，不作討論，但「違法與否」，則必須明確，<span style=\"color: red;\">政府是有責任証明警方當日設置「封瑣區」的警權法律依據，也有責任澄清，市民純綷進入或逗留在「封瑣區」是否違法。</span><br />\n<br />\n有網友回應意指「警察設置封鎖區是違法行為」，或指，警察豈非在任何情況下，都不可以設置封鎖區？這兩種看法都是過於極端和不現實，上到法庭一定比法官轟走。警察有責任履行法定職務，要履行便需採取一些措施，包括設置封鎖區。首先，措施要合法，<span style=\"color: red;\">包括合基本法和人權法，其次是必需和合理，如屬於因維持公共秩序措施，影響公民權利，則措施必須相稱。</span>無論如何，不可能一刀切指封鎖區便不對。然而，<span style=\"color: red;\">沒有具體的普遍性權力條文，警察便不可貿然設置封鎖區或將封鎖區等同必然禁地，特別是遇上市民有意或要求進入封鎖範圍，真誠為了行使示威權的目的，警察不可隨意拒絕，一定要嚴肅考慮，在合乎和平示威的原則下更不得阻止。</span><br />\n<br />\n其他自己睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1017539\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1017539&d=kT0D7NwRktyFNYuHQ%2Fv%2Bez4xCSFqVWWaKp6LAuIW5iI%3D&h=1cbb020e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1017539&h=87bebac7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1017539</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">我理解，「純綷」進入或逗留在「封鎖區」不足以構違法。但有「封鎖區」，一般是警察「做緊嘢」，即履行 19 項職責的其中一或多項，若進入或逗留在「封鎖區」，一碌葛咁企或坐係一邊，不構成「阻礙」警察辦公，不應違法。</span>但如果你係咁檔住差佬，四處走，攪到差佬做唔到嘢，這樣行為即使不在「封鎖區」內進行，都構成阻差辦公。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98b910e46d6173930b6ca653128b5f736f302721","tid":1601920,"uid":190817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T08:34:54.000Z","msg":"拉一拉"},{"pid":"d2220a9c778491c41eaa04011c41655fa13bb249","tid":1601920,"uid":190817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T08:35:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3def098a72693adda7757a900e2282b332ddb008","tid":1601920,"uid":190817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T08:37:02.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"0d55918ad181d42527ef320835ad93e39ec23017","tid":1601920,"uid":151313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T08:42:45.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"674325db64c3ff838763616d434f364ce1253413","tid":1601920,"uid":14333,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T08:42:55.000Z","msg":"雖然而家唔會理法律<br />\n但都幫推"},{"pid":"c36e7ba280e86f7c78da1d984aca2db8e77b86e4","tid":1601920,"uid":6981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T08:43:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e110a95ddc8178d03820f58569ef025adcecc64e","tid":1601920,"uid":281756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T08:44:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e575b15a90ff85e6650edb7bae4e0b0807633584","tid":1601920,"uid":1550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T08:44:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3616839632c9ae676f6bfe8b5837b773b4a6b067","tid":1601920,"uid":190817,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"674325db64c3ff838763616d434f364ce1253413","tid":1601920,"uid":14333,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T08:42:55.000Z","msg":"雖然而家唔會理法律<br />\n但都幫推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T08:47:58.000Z","msg":"但大家有必要知 佢設立條線要有根據<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋你唔係走來走去 根本入得封鎖線內"},{"pid":"b94e7fc7cafdb93ba9c585b9aad7cd58596c846a","tid":1601920,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T08:48:27.000Z","msg":"唔會理<br />\n即拉48"},{"pid":"83f29675844e762d7bb8d54398589f828e4d8808","tid":1601920,"uid":190817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b94e7fc7cafdb93ba9c585b9aad7cd58596c846a","tid":1601920,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T08:48:27.000Z","msg":"唔會理<br />\n即拉48"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T08:51:55.000Z","msg":"日後市民要追究全部無理的封鎖線"},{"pid":"59abb3779e3c2a31740ab8f98436ee2504435112","tid":1601920,"uid":190817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T08:59:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"95323a61a9591ac4298f3eba70f62877550807e8","tid":1601920,"uid":66828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T08:59:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"65190b46e4b9536e79105679b3d860ddc3350997","tid":1601920,"uid":190817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T09:00:45.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"d21ecb37b3cb238a81d3940e400a9eb30ef4d67d","tid":1601920,"uid":190817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T09:01:54.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"9e3adfa97368693a25d0f7613a2874d260e2da22","tid":1601920,"uid":126099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T09:02:39.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"72334389565e349a8e240f949eb646acd2640115","tid":1601920,"uid":190817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T18:01:55.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"04872857d5ca270e0e45489e953e729ea0273aad","tid":1601920,"uid":79085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20